{"tid":1245253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本台發現有速龍小隊隊員將肩章前後倒轉配戴","createTime":"2019-06-20T08:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:34:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b71b63eab739b2e669a44be00b58f563ca90d3d8","tid":1245253,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:33:09.000Z","msg":"本台發現有速龍小隊隊員將肩章前後倒轉配戴<br />\n20.06.2019 16:31<br />\n警方俗稱速龍小隊的特別戰術小隊，難以識別身份問題引起關注。本台翻查上星期三金鐘衝突現場照片，發現在同一個速龍小隊，有隊員在胸前背心位置配戴肩章，有隊員無配戴肩章，亦有隊員懷疑將肩章前後倒轉配戴，遮蓋官階及警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n保安局長李家超昨日在立法會回應質詢時，引述警方資料，指速龍小隊工作服是依據行動和戰術需要而設計，無位置可以展示警員編號。本台已向警方查詢，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1125758&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1125758%26csid%3D261_341&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=116fa022\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1125758&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"359d7dc7cd14b23ccad7b994bc22d5aae637586d","tid":1245253,"uid":161626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"c2ae5d2e515fb02b027d3cda164dad258b337e21","tid":1245253,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c07329aebc3f06d1317a92fc76cf3db26290f2","tid":1245253,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"比卡超：速龍小隊工作服是依據行動和戰術需要而設計，無位置可以展示警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n行動和戰術 = 打鳩你班仆街<br />\n所以無位置可以展示警員編號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/n